{"text_id":208552,"tokens":["In"," this"," study",","," we"," investigate"," the"," Kondo"," effect"," in"," an"," electron"," system"," dynamically"," coupled"," with"," local"," optical"," phonon","."," The"," Kondo"," effect"," is"," a"," fundamental"," phenomenon"," in"," condensed"," matter"," physics",","," characterized"," by"," the"," coupling"," of"," a"," localized"," spin"," with"," a"," surrounding"," sea"," of"," conducting"," electrons",","," leading"," to"," the"," formation"," of"," a"," many","-","body"," singlet"," state","."," Here",","," we"," consider"," a"," system"," in"," which"," the"," localized"," spin"," is"," further"," coupled"," to"," an"," optical"," phonon"," mode",","," resulting"," in"," a"," dynamic"," environment"," that"," can"," modulate"," the"," Kondo"," interaction",".","\n\n","The"," motivation"," for"," this"," research"," stems"," from"," the"," desire"," to"," understand"," and"," control"," the"," behavior"," of"," quantum"," impurity"," systems",","," which"," are"," of"," fundamental"," importance"," in"," the"," study"," of"," strongly"," correlated"," electron"," systems","."," By"," incorporating"," the"," dynamics"," of"," optical"," phon","ons",","," we"," aim"," to"," shed"," light"," on"," the"," role"," of"," phonon","-","assisted"," processes"," in"," the"," Kondo"," effect",","," as"," well"," as"," to"," explore"," the"," potential"," for"," novel"," physical"," phenomena",","," such"," as"," phonon","-","induced"," renormal","ization"," of"," the"," Kondo"," temperature"," and"," non","-","equilibrium"," behavior",".","\n\n","To"," tackle"," this"," problem",","," we"," employ"," a"," combination"," of"," analytical"," and"," numerical"," techniques",","," including"," the"," non","-","crossing"," approximation",","," numerical"," renormal","ization"," group",","," and"," time","-","dependent"," numerical"," renormal","ization"," group","."," These"," methods"," allow"," us"," to"," calculate"," the"," dynamical"," properties"," of"," the"," electron"," system",","," including"," the"," single","-","particle"," spectral"," function",","," the"," phonon"," spectral"," function",","," and"," the"," spin","-","spin"," correlation"," function",","," as"," a"," function"," of"," temperature",","," frequency",","," and"," optical"," phonon"," parameters",".","\n\n","Our"," results"," reveal"," a"," rich"," and"," complex"," behavior"," of"," the"," Kondo"," effect"," in"," the"," presence"," of"," optical"," phonon"," dynamics",","," highlighting"," the"," potential"," for"," new"," physical"," insights"," and"," applications"," in"," the"," study"," of"," strongly"," correlated"," electron"," systems","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"mixtral-8x7b","label":1}